CRYSTAL APPLIED said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 43.19% to NT$170,807,000 from NT$300,654,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            170,807          300,654    
YOY%             -43.19%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            676,639         1,266,516   
YOY%             -46.57% 
=================================================================
 